description: Are you a passionate leader with a deep commitment to Health and Wellness, and a proven ability to drive growth and develop high-performing teams? At KĀYA, we’re looking for two Club General Managers who can bring strategic focus, relational strength and commercial acumen to our thriving Melbourne (CBD) and Prahran (Chapel Street) locations. As KAYA embarks on a phase of transformation and growth with a new location set to open in November 2025, we’re on a search to find strong, people-first leaders who thrive in dynamic environments. An individual who is confident in developing culture and community as they are in delivering on commercial goals, driving membership growth and has a vision for cultivating people's futures. If you're ready to lead with heart, grow a thriving business and empower a passionate team, this could be your next chapter.
